i## 正确的操作		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i- 永远记住一点原则：OSPF，Babel 等 IGP（内部路由协议）不应处理 BGP 路		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i  由信息，BGP 路由就应该让 BGP 协议自己处理。		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i  - 在网络内部配置 BGP 有多种方案，可以参考		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
    《		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
1Bird 配置 BGP Confederation	/article/modify-website/bird-confederation.lantian/	{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i》i    这篇文章。		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i- 同时，内部路由协议的路由也不应漏到 BGP 中，除非内部路由协议中处理的		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i  所有 IP 段都是你自己所有。		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i- 所以你应该把 BGP 的 `export filter` 写成这样：		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i```bash		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
iexport filter {		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i  # 只允许向外发送来自 STATIC（手动配置）和 BGP 协议的路由		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i  if source ~ [RTS_STATIC, RTS_BGP] then accept;		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i  # 拒绝掉其它路由协议的路由		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i  reject;		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i}		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
